rComments: Very easy class, you don't feel overwhelmed by the information but at the end of the semester you've clearly improved your English! She's also pretty nice and approachable, and has A LOT of patience with her students! The homework/small assignments take little time to do, but you learn a lot! The class is small too, so it's really nice!
You have to do the homework. Really easy to pass the course. Great teacher, always available to her students.
